Detailed Description

template<class GDV1, PropCond p1, class GDV2, PropCond p2>
class Gecode::Graph::BinaryGraphPropagator< GDV1, p1, GDV2, p2 >

Base class for binary propagators (Update Gecode 2.1.1).

Allows the Implementation of a Binary Propagator whose Views are CpGraph Graph views for the implementation of a particular constraint.
